Name: Greg
AboutMe:
I've worked for several corporations, I'm currently a Software Engineer in the Portland, Oregon area. I'm attempting to create a non-profit to help children become more interested in software development and circuitry.

In my free time I try and contribute to several communities for technology, to help better share knowledge with peers in the industry.

My knowledge spans several languages, but I most frequently build corporate systems and E-Commerce solutions with Microsoft .Net, C#, SignalR, Web-Api, Html, Css, JavaScript, Knockout, and several other technologies.
